snowbound.api

Class SpawnAction

  • java.lang.Object
    • snowbound.api.SpawnAction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Action

    public class SpawnAction
extends Object
implements Action
    An action representing a unit spawning on the map. This action is considered valid when the unit is not spawned, the target exists, and the target is within your team's spawn locations.
